sentence: Joining forces for the 2003 parliamentary election, they achieved limited success, but more importantly managed to get into the coalition that formed the minority government (along with Democratic Party of Serbia, G17 Plus), providing it with critical parliamentary seats to keep the far-right radicals (Serbian Radical Party) at bay.
